   For Free | For Sale

   Publications

   Free Publications

   To order the following free publications, write the Federal Highway
   Administration (FHWA), Office of Transportation Operations (HOTO), 400
   7th Street, SW, Room 3416, Washington, DC 20590.

     Standard Alphabets for Highway Signs, 1966 Edition

     Standard Alphabets for Highway Signs and Pavement Markings, 1977
     Metric Edition

     Specifications for Standard Highway Sign Colors, May 1979.

   Publications for Sale

   The following publications can be ordered by mail from the Government
   Printing Office (GPO), Superintendent of Documents, P.O. Box 371954,
   Pittsburgh, PA 15250-7954. Make checks or money orders payable to
   Superintendent of Documents. To order by telephone, call 202-512-1800;
   fax 202-512-2250. VISA and MASTERCARD orders accepted by phone. For
   customer service information, call 202-512-1803.

   An online order form is available for the Standard Highway Signs Book.

     Standard Highway Signs Book, Stock No. 950-044-00000-4. $70
     (Domestic) and $87.50 (Foreign). Price includes subscription service
     for revisions. Two revisions are currently available. Order form

     Standard Specifications for Construction of Roads and Bridges on
     Federal-Aid Highways (FP-96) (1996 Edition), ISBN No. 0-16-053147-0.
     $28.

     NOTE: Hard copies of the MUTCD Millennium edition will not be
     available until Spring 2001. Cost information will be posted at that
     time.

   The following publications are available for purchase from other
   resources.

     Standard Color Tolerance Charts. $60 per color chart; $300 for set
     of 6 color charts. Contact: Hale Color Charts, Inc., 3709 Ocean View
     Avenue, Los Angeles, CA 90066. Telephone: 800-777-1225. On the Web
     at: www.halecolorcharts.com.

     Quality Standards for Work Zone Traffic Control Devices. $2.50 per
     copy for members, $3.75 per copy for nonmembers. Illustrates various
     condition levels of work zone devices Contact: ATTSA, 5440 Jefferson
     Davis Highway, Fredericksburg, VA 22407-2673, phone 540-898-5400;
     fax 540-898-5510. Discounts available for bulk quantities.

     Uniform Vehicle Code and Model Traffic Ordinance. Publication is
     designed as a comprehensive guide for developing standard state
     motor vehicle and traffic laws. It is based on experience under
     various state laws throughout the United States. Contact: National
     Committee on Uniform Traffic Laws and Ordinances, 107 S. West
     Street, # 110 Alexandria, VA 22314, Phone: 800-807-5290, FAX :
     540-465-5383.

     Railroad Highway Grade Crossing Handbook (Publication No.
     NTIS-PB-87-137527/AS), $28.95. Contact: National Technical
     Information Services (NTIS), 5285 Port Royal Road, Springfield, VA
     22161, telephone 703-487-4650.

   Many of the FHWA's partner organizations host on-line bookstores that
   sell publications directly. Contact:

   AASHTO
   http://www.aashto.org

   Institute of Transportation Engineers
   http://www.ite.org

   Transportation Research Board
   http://www.nationalacademies.org/trb/bookstore/
